          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1689.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Make the courgette salad</strong></p>\n<p>Peel the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of courgette 'ribbons'.</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> to a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>.<strong> </strong></p>\n<p>Add the<strong> courgette ribbons</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>courgette salad</strong>. </p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1689.-step-6-x200.jpg",
